## 📸 1. Executive Summary & Vision

<img align="right" alt="Coding GIF" width="380" src="https://cdn.dribbble.com/users/1162077/screenshots/3848914/programmer.gif" />

**MentiQ** is a groundbreaking, full-stack e-learning ecosystem designed to radically transcend traditional Learning Management Systems (LMS). Built upon a robust **Tri-Platform Architecture**—a React Native (Expo) Mobile application, a Vite (React 19) Web Portal, and an Enterprise Django Backend—MentiQ synchronizes education instantly and natively across all devices.

### 💡 The Core Vision

The ultimate goal of MentiQ is to democratize intelligence-driven education by:

* Streamlining and automating classroom management constraints.
* Personalizing learning at scale using real-time Generative AI.
* Providing unquestionable, fair assessments backed by intensely granular analytics.
* Enabling seamless financial and communication flow between administration, educators, and learners.

