## 🤖 2. The QBit AI Intelligence Center (Core Innovation)

<img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/73097560/115834477-dbab4500-a447-11eb-908a-139a6edaec5c.gif" width="100%" />

*The centerpiece of the MentiQ platform is our dedicated AI Hub, backed by the blazing-fast Llama 3 model queried via the Groq Cloud API.*

* **💬 Real-Time AI Tutor:** A highly context-aware conversational assistant acting as an on-demand tutor. It dynamically renders complex Markdown code snippets, mathematical equations, and logic explanations directly within the student's learning workflow.
* **🃏 Smart Flashcard Generation Engine:** Leverages Natural Language Processing (NLP) to dynamically generate spaced-repetition flashcard decks strictly based on course content and personalized syllabus structures.
* **📅 Premium Study Planner:** Parses user-selected subjects from an intuitive DataList UI to intelligently generate and structure weekly study timelines. This data flow culminates in polished, custom-styled PDFs exported securely.
* **📊 Knowledge Graph Analytics:** Recharts and D3-based graphs tracking student mastery over time by correlating `quiz_accuracy`, `time_spent`, and `flashcard_performance`.

