## 💳 4. Wallet & Payment Ecosystem Integration

MentiQ pushes beyond simple card processing by implementing an advanced inner-platform financial engine designed for emerging markets.

* **In-App Wallet WebView Integration:** Implemented an enterprise-grade Wallet engine utilizing a seamless WebView interface. Students can recharge their internal wallets instantly without leaving the native app.
* **Razorpay Order-Based State Tracking:** Wallet recharge and premium course tracking is executed through strict order-based webhook tracking tied securely to Razorpay, ensuring no dropped transaction states.
* **Unified Transaction Histories:** Transactions are synced asynchronously across the web and mobile interfaces dynamically updating user balances in a secured UI.

