## 🎥 5. Virtual Classrooms & The Assessment Engine

<img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/WUlplcMpOCEmTGBtBW/giphy.gif" width="40" /> <b>Real-Time Media & Operations</b>

* **🎬 Enterprise Video Integrations:** Zero-friction virtual classrooms utilizing Jitsi video wrappers embedded securely in WebViews. Native websocket chat persists throughout the stream.
* **📍 Auto-Attendance Engine:** The exact nanosecond a teacher updates classroom attendance, the data hits a backend API which invalidates the cache and pushes a live state update to the student's mobile dashboard.
* **💯 Advanced Anti-Cheat Protocol:** A rigorously enforced backend algorithm artificially caps online quizzes to a strict 3-attempt limit within a rolling 24-hour cycle.
* **📊 Micro-Level Quiz Grader:** Upon completion, the quiz result engine plots out exact submission diffs (what the student answered vs. the correct answer side-by-side using semantic diff logic).

