## 👑 6. Administrator & Enterprise Communication Center

The MentiQ Vite Web Portal contains a 14-page strictly administrative dashboard built primarily for oversight, mass communication, and granular interventions.

* **Personalised Direct Announcements:** Admins can target individual students with personalized, prioritized push notifications regarding attendance deficits, behavioral complaints, or bespoke academic updates directly from the Student Directory Table.
* **Campaign Systems & IMAP:** Capable of dispatching platform-wide HTML campaigns via Gmail SMTP routed through background Celery jobs to prevent main-thread blocking. Utilizing IMAP, student support replies are pulled back directly into the Admin Web Dashboard UI.
* **Real-Time Graphical Polling:** Complete platform-wide visualizations (Engagement KPIs, Student Progress Rings, Top Courses) crafted beautifully using Recharts.

